  "body": "<p>It's the first month as a design team member for <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/?aff=6cc2c70f\">Studio Calico</a> and I am pretty chuffed (an Australian term I have picked up) to show you a sneak at what I did with the Main kit, as well as Add-On's #1, 2, and 4. </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"15a-2ofus_2-600x429.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600645894747-FBANIIX4FK0J8LCTCZ7S/15a-2ofus_2-600x429.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"15b-4littlebooks_1-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600645895043-LGTGD025XJDXDYDLJELJ/15b-4littlebooks_1-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"15c-exhibitA_2-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600645895898-HD9LO26NP92RXMHI3XMO/15c-exhibitA_2-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"15d-homebody_2-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600645896442-LOS9L5PB6Q7RG5JYDRHZ/15d-homebody_2-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"15e-holla_1-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600645896624-CX5C64VA7AR5UFPF5R73/15e-holla_1-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>September <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/?aff=6cc2c70f\">Studio Calico</a> kit and Add-Ons available August 27th.</p>"
